name: Meme-me-1.0
tagline: A simple, fun meme generation app, created via Udacity course.
body:
### Welcome to Meme Me 1.0.
This app was coding entirely by your's truly, @NonCreature0714. It's a fun meme generating app which allows a use to create a meme then share with friends or save to a photo album. It's "1.0" because, you guessed it, there is a version 2.0. 

### Authors and Contributors
@NonCreature0714 (that's me!) wrote the code from this app in it's entirety.

### Support or Contact
Have a question about Meme Me 1.0? Email @NonCreature0714 at [noncreature0714@gmail.com](noncreature0714@gmail.com).
